        "ordinal": 30
      },
      "body_sha256": "42f19967725638ea5c8062bfe7a0e94267e8210d70e6af2d2080b2e0e75526a7",
      "body_chars": 224,
      "body_excerpt": "Of course, it does cost money for companies such as Sketch and Figma to duplicate features originating in Illustrator, and they have introdu"
    },
    {
      "gold_key": "t:numinous-ttft:margin-note-31",
      "kind": "margin_note",
      "label": "Margin note 32",
      "confidence": "strong",
      "extraction_method": "html_margin_note",
      "source_ref": {
        "format": "html",
        "fragment_idx": 0,
        "element": "span.marginnote",
        "ordinal": 31
      },
      "body_sha256": "e86bd29b8bd344901150ad0b0bcefa2b3b406e7b2db2c74654d81f9813000378",
      "body_chars": 851,
      "body_excerpt": "In fact, cloning is a real issue in gaming, especially in very technically simple games. An example is the game Threes, which took the devel"
    },
    {
      "gold_key": "t:numinous-ttft:margin-note-32",
      "kind": "margin_note",
      "label": "Margin note 33",
      "confidence": "strong",
      "extraction_method": "html_margin_note",
      "source_ref": {
        "format": "html",
        "fragment_idx": 0,
        "element": "span.marginnote",
        "ordinal": 32
      },
      "body_sha256": "e3a3818670662e4e46d70a0b9f3e6d067bd783c6762a666f3fd4c372ef8feb06",
      "body_chars": 452,
      "body_excerpt": "Programmer tools are a case where the insight-through-making loop operates quite well. The avoidance of the public goods problem is enabled "
    },
    {
      "gold_key": "t:numinous-ttft:margin-note-33",
      "kind": "margin_note",
      "label": "Margin note 34",
      "confidence": "strong",
